  "name": "pg_tre",
  "abstract": "Native PostgreSQL index access method for approximate regex matching",
  "description": "pg_tre provides a native index AM for fast approximate-regex queries over text columns. It uses a three-tier filter funnel (range bloom, trigram postings, per-tuple bloom) backed by the TRE library for recheck. Supports edit-distance k (insertions, deletions, substitutions) with configurable DoS protections.",
